                     <interp inst="t18340703-152-person963" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lodge at the Two Brewers, London Wall - I saw the prisoner running in London Wall - I heard the prosecutor crying, "Stop him! Stop him!" - the prisoner took the handkerchief from his bosom, and threw it away - I am not positive where he took it from - I took it up and gave it to Riley - I am sure it is the same.</p>
               <p>
            
