             (City police-constable, No.90). I live in Paul's Alley. I took charge of the prisoner with the handkerchief.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was walking along, and a young man pulled it down, and threw it over my shoulders - I took it off my shoulders, and put it in my bosom - the young man called, "Stop thief!" and I chucked it into the road.</p>
